Create Graded Page pt. 3 48

Step 1: Create Graded Page pt. 3

- Select the bottom left visual, change out the column values to Graded per Day and the line values to Avg days to grade (make sure you remove the periods in the title)

- Select formatting and change the title to Graded Per Day, Avg Days to Grade

- If your line has changed to a different color just go into data colors and change the Avg Days to Grade to the light blue color.
